<paragraph blockId="42.[151,1436,1348,1806]" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">
Distribution: Central-South Europe. In the Pollino mountains obviously a relictary element of springs at the highest elevations – no records from other South Italian mountain ranges, neither in 
<collectingRegion box="[1101,1197,1744,1770]" country="Italy" name="Calabria" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">Calabria</collectingRegion>
/ 
<collectingRegion box="[1206,1317,1744,1770]" country="Italy" name="Basilicata" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">Basilicata</collectingRegion>
, nor in the intensively studied Sicilian mountains.
</paragraph>
